-people-weakness-identification-tab" href="TA0019" aria-controls="v-people-weakness-identification" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">人员弱点识别</font></font></a><a class="nav-link side" id="v-organizational-weakness-identification-tab" href="TA0020" aria-controls="v-organizational-weakness-identification" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">组织弱点识别</font></font></a><a class="nav-link side active show" id="v-adversary-opsec-tab" href="TA0021" aria-controls="v-adversary-opsec" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">对手OPSEC </font></font></a><a class="nav-link side" id="v-establish-&amp;-maintain-infrastructure-tab" href="TA0022" aria-controls="v-establish-&amp;-maintain-infrastructure" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">建立和维护基础设施</font></font></a><a class="nav-link side" id="v-persona-development-tab" href="TA0023" aria-controls="v-persona-development" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">角色开发</font></font></a><a class="nav-link side" id="v-build-capabilities-tab" href="TA0024" aria-controls="v-build-capabilities" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">构建能力</font></font></a><a class="nav-link side" id="v-test-capabilities-tab" href="TA0025" aria-controls="v-test-capabilities" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">测试能力</font></font></a><a class="nav-link side" id="v-stage-capabilities-tab" href="TA0026" aria-controls="v-stage-capabilities" aria-selected="false"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">阶段能力</font></font></a>
